  stimulus_text = 'The scientist''s research showed that a small change in the amount of a certain chemical added to a solution could have a significant impact on the outcome of an experiment.  The scientist concluded that even though the change may seem minor, it can drastically affect the results. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
